definition: variant of 發怵|发怵[fa1 chu4]
to send out/to show (one's feeling)/to issue/to develop/to make a bundle of money/classifier for gunshots (rounds)

sentences.english: I was probably just as scared as everyone else, but inside I never felt better.
sentences.chinese: 我大概和別人一樣心裏發憷，不過心底我卻感覺很好。

sentences.english: She felt some apprehension at the thought of seeing him again.
sentences.chinese: 想到又要見他，她就感到有些發憷。
他那樣子實在是讓我發憷。
